enb_long_title: Twenty-sixth sessions of the Subsidiary Bodies (SB 26) of the United Nations Framework Convention on Climate Change (UNFCCC)
sentences: The Secretariat introduced this issue ( FCCC/SBI/2007/5 ).
The EU cautioned against creating additional reporting burdens.
Crispin d'Auvergne (Saint Lucia) and Helmut Hojesky (Austria) will hold consultations.
